title: Bunny Rabbit And Golden Retriever Have Hilarious Playtime Together
text:
Bunny Rabbit And Golden Retriever Have Hilarious Playtime Together   
When this Golden Retriever and pet white rabbit were playing in the backyard, their human pulled out their camera to record the fun. The dog’s tail doesn’t stop wagging and the bunny stands his ground, while pouncing and bouncing all over her! Said their human, “My dog and my bunny were playing in the back yard and I thought other people might enjoy watching as much as me.” 
Share this cute clip   friends! 
You may need to wait a few seconds for the video to appear.
